show.description: When simple and loving husband Kshitij is humiliated and betrayed by his ambitious wife Rakshita, he hides a shocking truth, he is actually Kshitij Maurya, heir to the billion-dollar Maurya Enterprises empire. As lies, blackmail, and revenge spiral out of control, Kshitij’s secret identity unleashes a storm that will destroy betrayals and rewrite destinies. Watch Now!
